religion and politics.

00:01:14.470 --> 00:01:16.590 align:middle line:84%
And I think it's really
valuable for people

00:01:16.590 --> 00:01:19.554 align:middle line:84%
to understand the genesis of
some of this thought, some

00:01:19.554 --> 00:01:20.470 align:middle line:90%
