how did you perceive

00:06:42.530 --> 00:06:44.660 align:middle line:84%
that part of his
role in the world,

00:06:44.660 --> 00:06:47.600 align:middle line:84%
to rewrite the Bible into
this everlasting, at least

00:06:47.600 --> 00:06:50.420 align:middle line:84%
the last few hundred years,
King James version of the Bible?

00:06:50.420 --> 00:06:52.170 align:middle line:84%
>>LOUV: Well, it's a
fascinating question.

00:06:52.170 --> 00:06:54.620 align:middle line:84%
And there was so much
going on at this time.

00:06:54.620 --> 00:06:57.620 align:middle line:84%
Those guys, both Bacon,
Shakespeare, John Dee,

00:06:57.620 --> 00:06:59.370 align:middle line:84%
of course, they were
all working together.

00:06:59.370 --> 00:07:02.090 align:middle line:10%
There was a lot going on behind
the scenes, some of which

00:07:02.090 --> 00:07:04.970 align:middle line:10%
is historically accepted and
some of which is conjecture.

00:07:04.970 --> 00:07:07.280 align:middle line:84%
But it's just very
clear to me, observing

00:07:07.280 --> 00:07:10.610 align:middle line:84%
that period in history, that
there was a group of very, very

00:07:10.610 --> 00:07:12.740 align:middle line:84%
intelligent people, a
real intelligentsia, who

00:07:12.740 --> 00:07:14.510 align:middle line:84%
were working with
everything they

00:07:14.510 --> 00:07:17.840 align:middle line:84%
had to modernize
Europe and bring

00:07:17.840 --> 00:07:24.650 align:middle line:84%
new ideas of spirituality, and
scientific advance, and world

00:07:24.650 --> 00:07:28.170 align:middle line:84%
exploration, and art, and drama,
in the case of Shakespeare,

00:07:28.170 --> 00:07:30.892 align:middle line:84%
and then, yes, the
modernization of the Bible.

00:07:30.892 --> 00:07:32.600 align:middle line:84%
And the fascinating
thing about all these

00:07:32.600 --> 00:07:35.300 align:middle line:84%
is the real common
thread with all of them

00:07:35.300 --> 00:07:39.080 align:middle line:84%
is the faith in the
liberation of human beings

00:07:39.080 --> 00:07:42.080 align:middle line:84%
from superstition and control,
the idea that human beings

00:07:42.080 --> 00:07:45.260 align:middle line:84%
should be free to
pursue happiness,

00:07:45.260 --> 00:07:48.470 align:middle line:84%
to pursue scientific truth,
to pursue religious truth

00:07:48.470 --> 00:07:49.850 align:middle line:90%
on their own terms.

00:07:49.850 --> 00:07:51.680 align:middle line:84%
Those are the ideas
that became America.

00:07:51.680 --> 00:07:54.320 align:middle line:84%
All of these things
were manifested finally

00:07:54.320 --> 00:07:56.741 align:middle line:84%
as the United States, which
was a project of these guys,

00:07:56.741 --> 00:07:57.740 align:middle line:90%
including Francis Bacon.

