to get it in context.

00:56:19.580 --> 00:56:20.970 align:middle line:84%
It's very opaque if you
don't know the context.

00:56:20.970 --> 00:56:23.320 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: I was going to say,
if you did all that in 10 pages,

00:56:23.320 --> 00:56:24.240 align:middle line:90%
