00:56:24.240 --> 00:56:26.170 align:middle line:84%
And I hear your book
is doing fabulously.

00:56:26.170 --> 00:56:26.950 align:middle line:90%
>>LOUV: It's doing very well.

00:56:26.950 --> 00:56:27.250 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

00:56:27.250 --> 00:56:29.230 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Wow, you went through
four printings, how quickly?

