>>REGINA: And thank
you for trying

00:56:35.346 --> 00:56:38.110 align:middle line:84%
to put some truth around
the legend of this man.

00:56:38.110 --> 00:56:39.209 align:middle line:90%
>>LOUV: Thank you.

